{"tid":2388822,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"【堅離地傾・沈旭暉 】 陳文敏：BNO的前世今生，中方反制有用嗎？(上)","createTime":"2021-01-31T12:04:30.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-31T17:17:55.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"f5e56f4aefde68ff6b5ba4299ee6138452d74aea","tid":2388822,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T12:04:30.000Z","msg":"【堅離地傾・沈旭暉 091🇬🇧🇭🇰】<br />\n陳文敏：BNO的前世今生，中方反制有用嗎？(上)<br />\nJan 31, 2021<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=0FLkC93U7Ek\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D0FLkC93U7Ek&d=%2FNwPZCYHbisYOb37lcvQWhvkGFRp1GVnGvdlwu1qkBE%3D&h=0bbc2c23\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=0FLkC93U7Ek</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n堅離地球 &middot; 沈旭暉<br />\n190K subscribers<br />\n<br />\n英國的BNO擴權政策正式落實，為香港人家庭開啟了無數可能，但也惹來中方聲稱要「強硬反制」。究竟英國的政策還有沒有變數？中方的反制成效如何？香港人應該如何回應這政策？由於相關資訊非常專業，但很容易被斷章取義的理解，我們特別邀請到研究BNO這議題數十年、目前身在英國的香港大學法學院前院長陳文敏教授，和我們詳細剖析。<br />\n<br />\nSimon 沈旭暉 堅離地 Social Media ▶<br />\n⏺Patreon: <a href=\"http://www.patreon.com/simonshen​​​\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.patreon.com%2Fsimonshen%E2%80%8B%E2%80%8B%E2%80%8B&d=%2FNwPZCYHbisYOb37lcvQWhvkGFRp1GVnGvdlwu1qkBE%3D&h=a7472dc1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.patreon.com/simonshen​​​</a><br />\n🔼Facebook: <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/shensimon​​​\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fshensimon%E2%80%8B%E2%80%8B%E2%80%8B&d=%2FNwPZCYHbisYOb37lcvQWhvkGFRp1GVnGvdlwu1qkBE%3D&h=74237f0a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/shensimon​​​</a><br />\nℹ️Instagram: <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/simon.diplo...​\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fsimon.diplo...%E2%80%8B&d=%2FNwPZCYHbisYOb37lcvQWhvkGFRp1GVnGvdlwu1qkBE%3D&h=982b82a5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/simon.diplo...​</a><br />\n➡️T